{
  "stem": "21308.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he invited me to the unveiling of a monument at Neustadt, on the beaches where these people were being murdered as they struggled ashore from the barges.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That is where Mrs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Feniger tells such a poignant story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She is the curator of the Holocaust Museum in Melbourne.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- then, in 1948, I returned to the United Kingdom.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, of course, I was now full-time serving.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, in 1949, I was sent as a part of a mobilizing force to Hong Kong, when Chiang Kai-shek was being kicked out of China.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was there for four years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I must say, they were four very happy years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then I came home from there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I went to Wales, training young British soldiers, nine national servicemen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Very good lads, they were.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Very good lads.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then I did my time there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then I went to Northumberland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was seconded to a territorial army regiment which was re-forming after the shake-up in the territorial army.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was with them for about 12 months.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was then sent to senior officer school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I did my course at the senior officer school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the-- then I went back to my territorial unit in Northumberland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then, all of a sudden, I was ordered to go and join a regular unit down at Pulford in the south of England.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And eventually, found myself in that regiment, mobilizing to go to Malaya, jungle-bashing, chasing communist bandits in the jungle.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But unfortunately, the Suez business blew up, so we got stuck in the Suez business.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there, to everlasting shame, the-- the whole thing was-- well, again, the Americans made nonsense of it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we still haven't got peace in that area.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
